<section class="py-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-center text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Before vs. after</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white text-center leading-tight mb-12">
      A different way to decide what ships.
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-[#0d1627] border border-[#1e2d4a] rounded-2xl p-8">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Before</p>
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Roadmap decisions driven by whoever spoke loudest in the last sprint meeting.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-950/40 to-[#0d1627] border border-blue-700/30 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">After</p>
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Every decision justified by real customer requests, weighted by revenue impact, traceable back to actual conversations. Your team knows why they're building every feature.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
